Lol, I love that Enchanter in Qeynos Hills.  I tried to kill him one day just to do it.  I would summon my pet, blast him and send my pet in after him.  He would charm me on the first spell and when charm broke, would walk away like nothing happened.  I would then have to zone in Surefall Glade and back into Qeynos Hills just so I could summon a pet again.  I did manage to kill him at one point.  I resisted his charm spells long enough for me to kill him.<P>--------------------<P>Jimm The Magician<BR>Magician of the 40th Season<BR>Luclin
